Title: toRelativeYearNum
Description: Converts a date, or date with time, to the number of years elapsed since a certain fixed point in the past.
date — Date or date with time. Date/DateTime/DateTime64.
The number of years from a fixed reference point in the past. UInt16.
Examples: SELECT    toRelativeYearNum(toDate('2002-12-08')) AS y1,    toRelativeYearNum(toDate('2010-10-26')) AS y2
